title: Rugged Raw 3
description:
We're stoked to present Rugged Raw 3 the latest full length video by that man Jake Martinelli! Filmed in London and its surrounding boroughs as well as San Francisco, Warsaw and various other locations. You already know we're huge fans of these boys and we highly recommend you crack a Holsten tinnie and appreciate this belter with amazing animations, soundtrack and cut scenes to boot!

Animations: George Coffey. 
Animation Titles: Tom Delves. 
Cover Design: George Coffey.
